AD_TAB.NAME: Assets

AD_TAB.HELP: Define assets owned by your company and create an amortization for them.

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create budgets for a selected year to be used for informative purposes.
AD_TAB.HELP: Create budgets for a selected year to be used for informative purposes.

AD_TAB.NAME: Import Business Partner Balance
AD_TAB.HELP: Import business partner balance, to enable you register the payment from/lto your business partner after opening balance. You may not enter the detail of invoice, but you define how much and when you need to receive/pay to your business partner. One business partner can have several due date and amount to be received/paid.

AD_TAB.NAME: Lines
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Add budget lines. Each line may refer to a specified period, business partner, product, etc.
AD_TAB.HELP: Add budget lines. Each line may refer to a specified period, business partner, product, etc.

AD_TAB.NAME: Asset Amortization
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Add asset amortizations for a selected asset.
AD_TAB.HELP: Add asset amortizations for a selected asset.

AD_TAB.NAME: Import Product Prices
AD_TAB.HELP: You may import product price after import product (product definition and product purchasing data, using import product window). You can import several prices for a product, 1 price for 1 price list. You can not import 2 price for same product at the same price list.

AD_TAB.NAME: Import Products Cost
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Import Product Cost to define the latest costing at the begining of accounting period
AD_TAB.HELP: Import Product Cost to define the latest costing at the begining of accounting period. By providing the product cost you are allowed to see the valued stock value, and also post the 1st Goods Receipt document. Beside that, you will get matched value of your inventory in the warehouse and in your balance sheet.

AD_TAB.NAME: Accounting
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create and edit G/L accounts to be used in transactions which include a selected asset.
AD_TAB.HELP: Create and edit G/L accounts to be used in transactions which include a selected asset.
